        <ul>
            <li>
                The agent of the reaction force is Jennifer.
            </li>
            <li>
                The object of the reaction force is the rope.
            </li>
            <li>
                The magnitude of the reaction force is 350 N.
            </li>
            <li>
                The direction of the reaction force is downward.
            </li>
        </ul>

    </li>
</ul>

